            "heading": "The Formula",
            "text": "<p><strong>Nature figured this out long before we did.</strong></p><p>Bees have been producing one of the most powerful natural antimicrobials on earth for millions of years. We just learned how to put it to work.</p><p>Our patent-pending beeswax infusion process creates a hand sanitizer that kills 99.9% of germs and — unlike every alcohol-based formula before it — actually protects and moisturizes your skin while it works. Made with organic ingredients. No mystery chemicals. Nothing you can't pronounce.</p><p>We call it Elevated Everyday Essentials. Smart formats, better ingredients, less fuss.</p>",
